Titolo: Chaos Control (video game)

Anno: 1995

Descrizione: Chaos Control is a rail shooter developed by Infogrames Multimedia and published by Philips Interactive Media for the CD-i, MS-DOS, Macintosh, Sega Saturn and PlayStation in 1995. The game's cutscenes are rendered in a style reminiscent of anime.An enhanced remake titled Chaos Control Remix was developed and published by Infogrames Multimedia exclusively for the Sega Saturn in 1996. It was released in PAL regions under the name Chaos Control, causing it to sometimes be confused with the original game.